          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Special Needs Tax Credit Act</strong></p> <p> This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow an income-based tax credit, up to $5,000 in a taxable year, for legal expenses paid to establish a legal guardianship of a disabled family member. </p>]]></text>
